---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="A little about this blog and the person writing it."
	pubDate={new Date()}
>
	<p>
		Hi, I'm Bekir. This is my corner of the internet — a blog about
		<em>anything</em>. Code I'm tinkering with, things I'm learning, and the odd
		late-night thought that's easier to write down than to keep rattling around.
	</p>

	<p>
		There's no single theme here on purpose. Some posts will be technical, some
		will be personal, and some will just be me thinking out loud. If that sounds
		like your kind of place, stick around.
	</p>

	<h2>What you'll find</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Notes on projects and the things I build</li>
		<li>Lessons learned the hard way</li>
		<li>Whatever's on my mind after dark</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		Want to say hi? The links in the header and footer are the best way to reach
		me. Thanks for reading. 🌙
	</p>
</Layout>
